Author: Michael Ting
Base Code: Dr. David Mould

Description:
  A spaceship AI script using finite state machines to destroy asteriods and targets. Goes from a hunting state where it will attempt
  to ram the closest asteriod. Then goes to the flee state where it will run away for a second. Then goes to the shoot state where it will
  shoot at the closest enemy before returning to the hunt state

Running:
  1. Open in visual studio
  2. In solution explorer click "Retarget Solution" on the project file.
  3. Run debugger to test

Using:
- C++ 11
- openGL 4.6
